//================================================
//  Windows
//================================================
1- Main:
	a- display main options:
		1- Add 		  2- displayAll 3- searchById 4- updateById
		5- deleteById 6- calcAvgGpa 7- getMaxGpa  8- Exit
	b- take user input

2- AddNewStudent:
	a- take user inputs:
		1- id 2- name 3- age 4- gpa
	b- ask if more or go to main
	
3- DisplayAllStudents:
	a- display in organized way
	b- ask if go to main
	 
4- SearchById:
	a- take id input
	b- show data if exits
	c- ask if new id or back to main
	
